source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_00<tab>789th Order Dustman Bo Zu fears that not all of his peers share an appreciation for slopwork and subterfuge.
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_00<tab>第789洞穴団の採掘地のダストマン789 ボ・ズは、不正がバレるのを恐れているようだ。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_01<tab>Showing once again that he will spare no effort in shirking honest work, 789th Order Dustman Bo Zu has padded his sack with rubbish and refuse to meet his daily mining quota. None the wiser, the 411th Order plans to smelt the 789th's yield in their furnace, and Bo Zu fears that his ingenuity will not be well received. At Bo Zu's request, consult with the acolyte Ba Go, that you might lay waste to the furnace before the dustman's duplicity comes to light.
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_01<tab>ダストマン789 ボ・ズは、上納品の鉱石の中に不純物を混ぜていたらしい。それを冶金担当の第411洞穴団が溶鉱炉で溶かした場合、不正がバレてしまう。溶鉱炉を破壊する方法について、第789洞穴団の採掘地の「アコライト789 バ・ゴ」から話を聞いてみよう。

source:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_02Ever eager to see destruction and disorder arise around him, Ba Go furnishes you with a bomb of considerable explosive power, along with instructions to carry it to your target─the 411th Order's furnace in the vicinity of Iron Lake─with all haste.

※Fail to complete your objective in the allotted span of time, and the limpet bomb will detonate, causing damage to you in the process.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_02アコライト789 バ・ゴから、溶鉱炉を破壊するためのリムペットボムを受け取った。アイアンレイクの「」に「リムペットボム」を設置しよう。

※運搬状態は、一定時間が過ぎると効果を失います。
　運搬の効果が切れる際、「リムペットボム」は爆発し、
　自分もダメージを受けてしまいます。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_03<tab>The 411th's furnace is no more, and Bo Zu's secret remains safe for another day. Search the embers that you might return the bomb core to its creator, though you have a suspicion the spirited fireball will not come quietly...
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_03<tab>リムペットボムを設置して、溶鉱炉を破壊した。付近に飛び散った「<var 28 ((EObj)) F61E93F101 /var>」を調べ、現れた「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20AB901 /var>」を討伐して「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E898401 /var>」を入手しよう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_04<tab>You have successfully quelled the limpet bomb's temper and extracted its core. Return it to Ba Go at the 789th Order Dig, with the futile hope that his future creations will not prove so hot to handle.
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_04<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20AB901 /var>から<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E898401 /var>を入手した。第789洞穴団の採掘地の「アコライト789 バ・ゴ」に「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E898401 /var>」を渡そう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_05<tab>Delighted to hear that his prized creation was every ilm as destructive as he had foreseen, Ba Go resolves to redouble his efforts in building bombs of even greater destructive power. For better or for worse, share the news of your success with Bo Zu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_05<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E898401 /var>を渡すと、アコライト789 バ・ゴは新たなボムを生み出せると満足そうだった。第789洞穴団の採掘地の「ダストマン789 ボ・ズ」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_06<tab>Bo Zu breathes a sigh of relief, your efforts having ensured that his chicanery will go undetected and unpunished. Convinced that any effort to extol the virtues of honest labor would fall upon deaf ears, you take your leave, hoping against hope that the dawdling dustman's next imposition on your services will be a more constructive one...
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SEQ_06<tab>ダストマン789 ボ・ズに溶鉱炉の破壊を報告したところ、不正がバレずに済み安堵していた。同時に、冒険者がいれば不正を続けられると、味をしめてしまったようだ。彼らの尻を叩きつつ、またの機会があれば協力しよう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_00<tab>Speak with 789th Order Acolyte Ba Go.
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_00<tab>アコライト789 バ・ゴと話す

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_01<tab>Set a limpet bomb at the 411th Order furnace near Iron Lake.
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_01<tab>アイアンレイクの<var 28 ((EObj)) F61E93EE01 /var>にリムペットボムを設置

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_02<tab>Obtain a limpet bomb core from the embers.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_02を調べてから
を入手

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_03<tab>Deliver the limpet bomb core to 789th Order Acolyte Ba Go.
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_03<tab>アコライト789 バ・ゴに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E898401 /var>を渡す

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_04<tab>Report to 789th Order Dustman Bo Zu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_TODO_04<tab>ダストマン789 ボ・ズに報告

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_000<tab>Shiny metals are not easy to find─no, no, hide from Bo Zu's pick, they do. When I tire of working, I fill my sack with rocks and rubble instead. Does inspector notice? Not until Bo Zu is far away─far, far in the distance. Yes, Bo Zu is sharp like that─smart, quick, sharp.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_000マズいーど……マズすぎることになったーど。
このあいーだ　仕事のノルマを達成できなくーて
鉱石に　ただの石コロを混ぜーて　上納したんだーど……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_001<tab>411th Order metalworkers are not so sharp. No, no, they are dull indeed. They would smelt my ore in their furnace. Do they not realize the perils of such an action─the dangers, the risks, the perils?
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_001その鉱石を　冶金担当の石頭な「第411洞穴団」が
溶鉱炉で溶かしーて　使おうとしてるーど。
このままだと　ズルしたのがバレちゃうーど！

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_002<tab>No, no, their recklessness must be stopped─halted, disrupted, stopped─and now. Fortunately, Bo Zu knows exactly what must be done─precisely, specifically, exactly.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_002こうなったーら　使われてバレる前に
「アイアンレイク」の「」を
壊すしかないーど！

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_003<tab>We must use Ba Go's beauties to make furnace go boom. That will teach the futility of expecting real work from Bo Zu─the pointlessness, the fruitlessness, the futility. Yes, yes, that will teach them to let Bo Zu be Bo Zu.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_003「アコライト789 バ・ゴ」の力を借りるーど。
アイーツなら　溶鉱炉を壊せる爆弾　持ってそうだーど！

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_004<tab>We must use Ba Go's beauties to make furnace go boom. That will teach the futility of expecting real work from Bo Zu─the pointlessness, the fruitlessness, the futility. Yes, yes, that will teach them to let Bo Zu be Bo Zu.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_004「アコライト789 バ・ゴ」の力を借りるーど。
アイーツなら　溶鉱炉を壊せる爆弾　持ってそうだーど！

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_010<tab>Bo Zu would make furnace go boom, hide his trickery? Ba Go cares not for the dustman's fate─no, no, cares not at all─but needs no excuse for fiery fulminations. Yes, yes, Ba Go will help you.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_010ククク……「」を壊したーい？
面白いコート　考えるーね。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_011<tab>Ba Go will introduce you to his most buxom beauty. Beautiful indeed she is, yes, if a bit testy─ill-tempered, irascible, testy.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_011だったーら……ククク……
この「リムペットボム」ちゃんの　出番かーな？
ククク……破壊力は　ボクちゃん　折り紙つきーよ。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_012<tab>You would be wise to escort her to your destination with speed─haste, quickness, speed. Yes, yes─you will be wise, or you will be the one to go boom. Haha! Heaheaheahehahaha!
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_012ただーし　とっても繊細なのーね。
早く「」に　置いて逃げないーと
チミごとドッカーン　ダイバクハーツ……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_013<tab>And your task does not end when the furnace blows its top─no, no, it has only begun. You must bring Ba Go's beauty back, bring back what remains of her─her essence, her soul, her core.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_013……それーと　使い終わったーら　「」調べるーよ。
猛り狂った「」がいるかーら
やっつけーて　「」を回収するこーと。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_014<tab>But be forewarned─advised, cautioned, forewarned─Ba Go's beauties often have a mind of their own. Yes, yes, they do...
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_014心核あればー　また爆弾ちゃん　作れるーね。
もったいないかーら　再利用するーよ……ククク……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_015<tab>You must bring Ba Go's beauty to your destination with speed─haste, quickness, speed. Yes, yes─you will go quickly, or you will go boom. Haha! Heaheaheahehahaha!
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_015ククク……「リムペットボム」ちゃんが　爆発する前に
アイアンレイクの「」に置くんだーよ。
早くしないーと　チミごとドッカーン　ダイバクハーツ……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_016<tab>But your task does not end when the furnace blows its top─no, no, it has only begun. You must bring Ba Go's beauty back, bring back what remains of her─her essence, her soul, her core. But be forewarned: she has a mind of her own. Yes, yes, she does.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_016……それーと　使い終わったーら　「」調べるーよ。
猛り狂った「」がいるかーら
やっつけーて　「」を回収するこーと。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_017<tab>Adventurer is looking ashen─dusty, smoldery, ashen. Ba Go's beauty went boom on adventurer? Yes, yes, she did? Haha! Heahehaheaehahaha! Ba Go will give adventurer another beauty, if adventurer would make more booms. Yes, yes, more booms!
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_017ククク……失敗しちゃーった？
ドッカーン　ダイバクハーツ……クククククク……。
「リムペットボム」ちゃん　また持っていくかーい？

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_018<tab>Adventurer returns empty-handed? Yes, yes, <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> does? Adventurer would suffer same fate as Bo Zu? No, no, <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> would not? Then adventurer should retrace <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> steps─retread, repeat, retrace─and return with Ba Go's beauty.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_018ククク……ボムちゃんの　ご機嫌どうだーった？
ちゃんと「」調べーて　あらわれた
「」から「」を回収するこーと。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_020<tab>Where is she? Yes, where is Ba Go's beauty?
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_020ククク……溶鉱炉を無事に　壊せたみたいだーね。
「」を　もらおうーか？

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_021<tab>Ba Go's beauty returns─yes, yes, she does. Many booms were had, yes? Many shouts, many cries, many screams?
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_021ククク……リムペットボムちゃんは
ボクちゃんの　たいせつーな　たからもーの……。
この心核があれーば　また新たなボムちゃんが生み出せるーよ……

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_022<tab>And who are you again? You are who? Bo Zu's friend? Go back to Bo Zu, and tell him next time he bothers me, he will be the one to go boom. Heahehahehaehahaha!
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BAGO_000_022じゃあ　ボ・ズによろしーく。
また溶鉱炉　壊したいときーは
声かけるといいーよ……ククク……。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_030<tab>The 411th's furnace is no more? Bo Zu thanks you for your aid. You are a friend to slugs and slubbers everywhere─an ally, a patron, a friend.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_030アンータなかなか　できるヤツだーど。
これで　溶鉱炉のことーは　心配いらなくなったーど！

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_031<tab>Yes, yes, Bo Zu can look forward to many, many days of rest─rest and relaxation. You will linger close by, yes─stay, sojourn, linger? Today is a happy day, happy indeed!
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_BOZU_000_031……オイーラたち　こういう手抜き　結構やってるーど。
でもアンータの助けあれば　次も心配いらないどー！

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_POPMESSAGE_000_001<tab>There is a rush of heat from among the embers!

target: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_POPMESSAGE_000_002<tab>その行動は出現した敵を倒さないと実行できません

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SYSTEM_000_040<tab>You are not carrying the specified object. Return to the starting point and reattempt the delivery.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SYSTEM_000_040指定された運搬状態でなければ効果はありません。
開始地点に戻ると、再び運搬状態になります。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SYSTEM_000_050<tab>Transport the limpet bomb to the specified location at Iron Lake before it detonates.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SYSTEM_000_050「リムペットボム」を持ち上げて、制限時間内に、
アイアンレイクの「」まで運搬して
設置しましょう。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SYSTEM_000_051<tab>You will have sixty seconds to complete the task. Should you fail, return to the starting location and begin anew.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SYSTEM_000_051運搬状態の効果時間は「60秒」です。
時間切れになった場合、運搬は失敗になりますが、
開始地点から再挑戦することができます。

source: TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SYSTEM_000_052<tab>Be wary of attacks from enemies, which will sap your strength. Should you fail to complete the task in time, the bomb will explode and you will suffer damage.
target:
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_SYSTEM_000_052なお、攻撃を受けると、効果時間が減ってしまいます。
時間切れになると「リムペットボム」は爆発し、
自分もダメージを受けてしまうため、気をつけてください。
TEXT_BANKOB110_01334_Q1_000_000<tab>「リムペットボム」の運搬を開始しますか？
